results.notes: Several configuration keys from the canonical list are completely absent from the provided PDF pages. For keys that are present, some have minor discrepancies in description detail or units. A significant issue is the absence or incompleteness of enumeration tables in the PDF for several E1-type keys, making full validation impossible for those entries. There is also a notable discrepancy in the description and unit for CFG-NAVSPG-OUTFIL_TACC, suggesting a potential error in one of the sources.
